{"tid":429842,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"情困男雙刀架頸圖跳樓","createTime":"2017-10-09T09:52:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-09T10:06:42.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"72ab004f4417fa386f7eae92b570396e32d8bfed","tid":429842,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T09:52:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20176770&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20171009\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20176770%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20171009&d=KBe1arX0TEC7Xq1RNJa2Oo9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=33e5efd9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20176770%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20171009&h=fe27ae45\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20176770&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20171009</a><br />\n<br />\n情困男雙刀架頸圖跳樓<br />\n<br />\n港聞   <br />\n         <br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20171009/large/a0702a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20171009%2Flarge%2Fa0702a.gif&h=aa281441&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n警員穿上「鐵甲威龍」裝備登樓營救企圖跳樓男子（小圖）。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】一名男子昨晨在上水一貨倉內，用微博與女友交談期間，疑因感情問題發生爭執，突情緒激動，竟取出兩柄菜刀架頸，行近窗邊企圖跳樓，並自行報警指稱因不開心欲尋死。警方接報大為緊張，穿上「鐵甲威龍」裝備的警員登門營救，稍後由救援人員將事主拉回安全位置，惟他卻意外撞傷，口部流血要送院敷治。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n獲救時撞傷嘴送院<br />\n<br />\n現場為上水新運路188號劍橋廣場一化妝品倉庫，昨晨10時許，姓蘇（33歲）男子在貨倉內，以電腦用微博與女友交談期間，雙方疑因感情問題發生爭執，蘇情緒激動，手持兩把菜刀架頸，並站近窗邊企圖跳樓，他自行報警，聲稱欲跳樓自殺。<br />\n<br />\n警員及消防員到場救援，警方衝鋒隊人員穿起鐵甲威龍全副裝備，帶同盾牌登樓，最後救援人員趁事主不為意，將他拉回安全位置，惟蘇意外撞到硬物，口部流血受傷，救護員遂將他送院敷治。<br />\n<br />\n■記者文兆麟"},{"pid":"e045e5ef5adac63bb8e9ddb692621977857b5c05","tid":429842,"uid":2267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T09:58:09.000Z","msg":"垃圾"},{"pid":"11a05f5392acd3865c106b2f211c567de7a0fac6","tid":429842,"uid":28480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T09:59:37.000Z","msg":"自殺報警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a852d14906be037b9f54d5d7b5ee513155592648","tid":429842,"uid":124114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T10:00:45.000Z","msg":"自已報警LOL"},{"pid":"0c2bf1ddc7b1e20e80d47cc36e59ead5138e2ce2","tid":429842,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T10:06:42.000Z","msg":"垃圾大陸佬"}]}